                <head>51. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>On July 18, the Council of Delegates of the Inter-American Defense Board approved
                    in Washington a revised joint military defense plan for the Western Hemisphere.
                    No copy of the plan has been found in Department of State files.</p>
            </div>
